#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:10:"Kathryn P.";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5208:"<p>We have a November treat for theme-lovers – a slew of new free themes by Automattic designers and theme wranglers have made their debut on WordPress.org. Meet the fabulous five:</p>\n<p>Crafted by<a href="http://carolinemoore.net/"> Caroline Moore</a>,<a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/affinity/"><strong> Affinity</strong></a> features an elegant multi-panel scrolling front page. Geared to weddings and family announcements, it&#8217;s flexible enough to suit a wide variety of sites.</p>\n<p><a href="https://affinitydemo.wordpress.com/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6688" src="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=840&#038;h=883" alt="Affinity screenshot" width="840" height="883" srcset="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=840&amp;h=883 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=143&amp;h=150 143w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=285&amp;h=300 285w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=768&amp;h=808 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=974&amp;h=1024 974w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg 1665w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /></a></p>\n<p><a href="https://thomasguillot.com/">Thomas Guillot</a> designed <a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/shoreditch/"><strong>Shoreditch</strong></a> especially for businesses who want to easily combine multiple panels on any page.</p>\n<p><a href="https://shoreditchdemo.wordpress.com/"><img class="alignnone wp-image-6685" src="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=840&#038;h=959" alt="Shoreditch screenshot" width="840" height="959" srcset="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg 720w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=131&amp;h=150 131w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=263&amp;h=300 263w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /></a></p>\n<p>Looking for a fresh new blogging-focussed theme? Check out our trio:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A modern blogging theme that shows off gorgeous photography, <a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/revelar/"><strong>Revelar</strong></a> is designed by <a href="http://mutelife.com/">Filipe Varela</a> and developed by <a href="https://soakingupthelight.wordpress.com/">Ola Bodera</a>;</li>\n<li><a href="http://diaryofawebsite.com/">Tammie Lister</a>&#8216;s <strong><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/cols/">Cols</a></strong> features a minimalist multi-column text display; and</li>\n<li><strong><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/lyretail/">Lyretail</a>,</strong> designed by <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/melchoyce/">Mel Choyce</a> and developed by Caroline Moore, is a clean single-column theme for personal bloggers with prominent social links in the header.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Take your favorite for a spin today!</p>\n<p><a href="https://revelardemo.wordpress.com/"><img class="imgborder alignnone wp-image-6690" src="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=840&#038;h=630" alt="Revelar screenshot" width="840" height="630" srcset="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png 720w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=150&amp;h=113 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=300&amp;h=225 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /></a></p>\n<p><a href="https://colsdemo.wordpress.com/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6691" src="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/cols-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=630" alt="Cols screenshot" width="840" height="630" srcset="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/cols-ss.png?w=840&amp;h=630 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/cols-ss.png?w=150&amp;h=113 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/cols-ss.png?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/cols-ss.png?w=768&amp;h=576 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/cols-ss.png 880w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /></a></p>\n<p><a href="https://lyretaildemo.wordpress.com/"><img class="alignnone wp-image-6692" src="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/lyretail-ss1.jpg?w=840&#038;h=630" alt="Lyretail screenshot" width="840" height="630" srcset="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/lyretail-ss1.jpg 720w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/lyretail-ss1.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/lyretail-ss1.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /></a></p><img alt="" border="0" src="https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6674&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:53:"https://themeshaper.com/2016/11/07/theme-o-rama/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s